Global High Performance Liquid Chromatography (HPLC) Assay Kits Market Insights
High Performance Liquid Chromatography (HPLC) Assay Kits Market size was valued at USD 1.20 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.85 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.05% from 2024 to 2030.

High Performance Liquid Chromatography (HPLC) Assay Kits Market Overview
The global High Performance Liquid Chromatography (HPLC) Assay Kits market size was valued at USD 4.2 billion in 2024 and is expected to expand at a CAGR of 7.1% from 2025 to 2032. HPLC is a crucial technology used in pharmaceutical, biotechnological, and chemical industries for qualitative and quantitative analysis of various compounds. The increasing demand for advanced analytical techniques, coupled with the rapid growth of the healthcare and pharmaceutical industries, is driving the market growth. Additionally, HPLC's wide applications in diagnostics, drug development, and environmental testing are further bolstering its adoption.

